{"ja458:0.1":"Jataka ","ja458:0.2":"Ekadasakanipata ","ja458:0.3":"Matuposakavagga ","ja458:0.4":"4. Udayajataka ","ja458:1.1":"“Eka nisinna suci sannaturu, ","ja458:1.2":"Pasadamaruyha aninditangi; ","ja458:1.3":"Yacami tam kinnaranettacakkhu, ","ja458:1.4":"Imekarattim ubhayo vasema”. ","ja458:2.1":"“Okinnantaraparikham, ","ja458:2.2":"dalhamattalakotthakam; ","ja458:2.3":"Rakkhitam khaggahatthehi, ","ja458:2.4":"duppavesamidam puram. ","ja458:3.1":"Daharassa yuvino capi, ","ja458:3.2":"agamo ca na vijjati; ","ja458:3.3":"Atha kena nu vannena, ","ja458:3.4":"sangamam icchase maya”. ","ja458:4.1":"“Yakkhohamasmi kalyani, ","ja458:4.2":"Agatosmi tavantike; ","ja458:4.3":"Tvam mam nandaya bhaddante, ","ja458:4.4":"Punnakamsam dadami te”. ","ja458:5.1":"“Devam va yakkham atha va manussam, ","ja458:5.2":"Na patthaye udayamaticca annam; ","ja458:5.3":"Gaccheva tvam yakkha mahanubhava, ","ja458:5.4":"Ma cassu gantva punaravajittha”. ","ja458:6.1":"“Ya sa rati uttama kamabhoginam, ","ja458:6.2":"Yam hetu satta visamam caranti; ","ja458:6.3":"Ma tam ratim jiyi tuvam sucimhite, ","ja458:6.4":"Dadami te rupiyam kamsapuram”. ","ja458:7.1":"“Narim naro nijjhapayam dhanena, ","ja458:7.2":"Ukkamsati yattha karoti chandam; ","ja458:7.3":"Vipaccaniko tava devadhammo, ","ja458:7.4":"Paccakkhato thokatarena esi”. ","ja458:8.1":"“Ayu ca vanno ca manussaloke, ","ja458:8.2":"Nihiyati manujanam sugatte; ","ja458:8.3":"Teneva vannena dhanampi tuyham, ","ja458:8.4":"Nihiyati jinnatarasi ajja. ","ja458:9.1":"Evam me pekkhamanassa, ","ja458:9.2":"rajaputti yasassini; ","ja458:9.3":"Hayateva tava vanno, ","ja458:9.4":"ahorattanamaccaye”. ","ja458:10.1":"“Iminava tvam vayasa, ","ja458:10.2":"rajaputti sumedhase; ","ja458:10.3":"Brahmacariyam careyyasi, ","ja458:10.4":"bhiyyo vannavati siya”. ","ja458:11.1":"“Deva na jiranti yatha manussa, ","ja458:11.2":"Gattesu tesam valiyo na honti; ","ja458:11.3":"Pucchami tam yakkha mahanubhava, ","ja458:11.4":"Katham nu devana sariradeho”. ","ja458:12.1":"“Deva na jiranti yatha manussa, ","ja458:12.2":"Gattesu tesam valiyo na honti; ","ja458:12.3":"Suve suve bhiyyatarova tesam, ","ja458:12.4":"Dibbo ca vanno vipula ca bhoga”. ","ja458:13.1":"“Kimsudha bhita janata aneka, ","ja458:13.2":"Maggo ca nekayatanam pavutto; ","ja458:13.3":"Pucchami tam yakkha mahanubhava, ","ja458:13.4":"Katthatthito paralokam na bhaye”. ","ja458:14.1":"“Vacam mananca panidhaya samma, ","ja458:14.2":"Kayena papani akubbamano; ","ja458:14.3":"Bahunnapanam gharamavasanto, ","ja458:14.4":"Saddho mudu samvibhagi vadannu; ","ja458:14.5":"Sangahako sakhilo sanhavaco, ","ja458:14.6":"Etthatthito paralokam na bhaye”. ","ja458:15.1":"“Anusasasi mam yakkha, ","ja458:15.2":"yatha mata yatha pita; ","ja458:15.3":"Ularavannam pucchami, ","ja458:15.4":"ko nu tvamasi subraha”. ","ja458:16.1":"“Udayohamasmi kalyani, ","ja458:16.2":"sangaratta idhagato; ","ja458:16.3":"Amanta kho tam gacchami, ","ja458:16.4":"muttosmi tava sangara”. ","ja458:17.1":"“Sace kho tvam udayosi, ","ja458:17.2":"sangaratta idhagato; ","ja458:17.3":"Anusasa mam rajaputta, ","ja458:17.4":"yathassa puna sangamo”. ","ja458:18.1":"“Atipatati vayo khano tatheva, ","ja458:18.2":"Thanam natthi dhuvam cavanti satta; ","ja458:18.3":"Parijiyyati addhuvam sariram, ","ja458:18.4":"Udaye ma pamada carassu dhammam. ","ja458:19.1":"Kasina pathavi dhanassa pura, ","ja458:19.2":"Ekasseva siya anannadheyya; ","ja458:19.3":"Tancapi jahati avitarago, ","ja458:19.4":"Udaye ma pamada carassu dhammam. ","ja458:20.1":"Mata ca pita ca bhataro ca, ","ja458:20.2":"Bhariya yapi dhanena hoti kita; ","ja458:20.3":"Te capi jahanti annamannam, ","ja458:20.4":"Udaye ma pamada carassu dhammam. ","ja458:21.1":"Kayo parabhojananti natva, ","ja458:21.2":"Samsare sugatinca duggatinca; ","ja458:21.3":"Ittaravasoti janiyana, ","ja458:21.4":"Udaye ma pamada carassu dhammam”. ","ja458:22.1":"“Sadhu bhasatiyam yakkho, ","ja458:22.2":"appam maccana jivitam; ","ja458:22.3":"Kasiranca parittanca, ","ja458:22.4":"tanca dukkhena samyutam; ","ja458:22.5":"Saham eka pabbajissami, ","ja458:22.6":"hitva kasim surundhanan”ti. ","ja458:23.1":"Udayajatakam catuttham. "}